msgid "Scenario VIII: Return to Dim Carcosa"
msgstr "冒险VIII：重返卡城幽影"

msgid "Put Shores of Hali, Dark Spires, and Palace of the King <i>(Hastur's Domain)</i> into play. Remove the old copy of Palace of the King from the game."
msgstr "将哈利湖滨、黑色尖柱、王之宫殿<i>(哈斯塔的领域)</i>放置进场。将原版的王之宫殿地点从游戏中移除。"

msgid "Set the following locations aside, out of play: Recesses of Your Own Mind, The Throne Room, and Stage of the Ward Theatre."
msgstr "将下列地点放在一边，位于场外：内心深处、王座大厅和沃德剧院舞台。"

msgid ""
"For the duration of this scenario, the following additional rules apply:\n"
"\"Hastur's health cannot be reduced to less than 2 [per_investigator] unless any investigator 'knows the secret.'\"\n"
"Attach the Return to Dim Carcosa scenario reference card to the scenario reference card as a reminder."
msgstr ""
"在本场冒险接下来的时间里，增加以下额外规则：\n"
"“除非‘调查员知道了秘密’，否则哈斯塔的生命值不能被减少到低于2[per_investigator]。”\n"
"将重返卡城幽影冒险辅助卡叠加到冒险辅助卡，以作提示。"
